      </div>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-light-muted dark:text-dark-muted"><code>npm run build</code> regenerates this report. It checks contrast, color-vision simulation, target sizes, overlap, and overflow across the representative routes.</p>
      <iframe class="mt-8 h-[42rem] w-full rounded-2xl border border-light-border bg-white dark:border-dark-border dark:bg-dark-surface" src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}development/ux/index.html`} title="Latest LibreUni UX report">
