          Enable the live theme customizer and element inspector. When enabled, a floating <code class="bg-primary/10 text-primary px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-black">+</code> button will appear in the bottom-right corner of all pages.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
          <button id="toggle-dev-tools" class="btn-secondary !rounded-xl !px-6 !py-3 text-sm font-black transition-all">
            Enable Developer Tools
