        <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-sm leading-relaxed text-light-muted dark:text-dark-muted">PCA reduces descriptive course metrics into principal components. The plots show patterns and outliers in course size and structure; they are not quality ratings.</p>

        <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">
